<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-bs-theme="light">

<head>
    <title>Simon Game - Liad Firouz</title>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
        <style>
            .project-hero {
                background-color: #f8f9fa;
                padding: 4rem 0;
            }

            .tech-box {
                background-color: #f1f3f5;
                border-left: 5px solid #ffc107;
                padding: 1.5rem;
                margin: 2rem 0;
            }
        </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
        <main class="container py-5">
            <div class="project-hero text-center mb-5 rounded">
                <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold">Simon Memory Game</h1>
                <p class="lead text-muted">Interactive JavaScript Logic & DOM Manipulation</p>
                <a href="https://liadfirouz.github.io/Simon-Game/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-dark btn-lg mt-3">Play
                    the Game</a>
            </div>
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-lg-8">
                    <h3>The Challenge: Logical State Management</h3>
                    <p>The Simon Game was an exercise in managing application state. Ensuring that the game sequence
                        flows correctly while updating the UI in real-time taught me how to handle event-driven
                        architecture and asynchronous logic effectively.</p>

                    <div class="tech-box">
                        <h5 class="fw-bold">Core Technologies:</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>State Management:</strong> Tracking game sequences and player inputs.</li>
                            <li><strong>DOM Manipulation:</strong> Dynamic UI updates and responsive visual feedback.
                            </li>
                            <li><strong>Event Listeners:</strong> Creating a seamless, interactive user experience.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center mt-5"><a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-dark">← Back to Portfolio</a></div>
        </main>
        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>